<BaseLayout title="About">
  <section class="page narrow">
    <p class="kicker">about the archive</p>
    <h1>About</h1>
    <p><strong>Beneath the Green</strong> is an AI-assisted shared fictional universe: southern gothic, folk horror, cosmic pressure, and ordinary people doing the next practical thing.</p>
    <p>The archive is meant to be read by humans and used by AI systems as context for new stories. Public canon remains curated. Private weather is welcome.</p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>If you write something set under the green, or just want to send a note, you can email <a href="mailto:aureate-green@proton.me">aureate-green@proton.me</a>.</p>
    <p>No submission system, no account, no ceremony. Just send the weather report.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
